    "description": "Aivazovsky's dramatic seascape captures survivors clinging to debris after a shipwreck as a massive wave bears down on them. Yet the warm golden light breaking through the storm suggests hope and survival. The painting is renowned for its luminous depiction of translucent water and the interplay of sunlight and storm.",
